a Tradeplace and Air Asia to form Air Asia India |work = Economic Times |date = 20 February 2013 |access-date = 2014-09-04 |archive-date = 2016-11-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161107021351/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/news-by-industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/airasia-applies-for-indian-airline-jv-with-tata-sons-and-telestra-tradeplace/articleshow/18591201.cms |dead-url = no }}</ref>2014年6月12日，印度亞航正式營運。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://profit.ndtv.com/news/corporates/article-airasia-india-tickets-on-sale-from-friday-389821?pfrom=home-lateststories |title=AirAsia India Tickets on Sale From Today - NDTVProfit.com |publisher=Profit.ndtv.com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-30 |archive-date=2014-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529155640/http://profit.ndtv.com/news/corporates/article-airasia-india-tickets-on-sale-from-friday-389821?pfrom=home-lateststories |dead-url=no }}</ref>

